Spragueanella bụ ụdị osisi na-agbasa okooko nke ezinụlọ Loranthaceae.
Ebe a mụrụ ya bụ akụkụ ọwụwa anyanwụ na ndịda nke Ebe okpomọkụ Afrika, n'ime mba Kenya, Malawi, Mozambique, Tanzania, Zambia na Zimbabwe.

Aha ụdị nke Spragueanella bụ iji sọpụrụ Thomas Archibald Sprague (1877-1958), onye Scottish botanist. 
A kọwara ya na mbụ ma bipụta ya na Bull
Nzukọ Ndị Isi Roy Colon Belge Vol.25 na peeji nke 1632 na 1954.
